{"tid":1463112,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「愛」字團體尖沙咀升旗　噴「殺他死」促警嚴正執法","createTime":"2019-08-13T12:09:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T12:14:17.000Z","uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ac881c08db28eb5e402ef07a772ca0011ac1b094","tid":1463112,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:09:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3155221/org/14a474f39155fb73f5582d5a2c2a539d.jpg/9VvyHEmzcGfM-duhwUoTS_cldzU7ZKMo9KHg6fSh4Ok?v=w1600r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3155221%2Forg%2F14a474f39155fb73f5582d5a2c2a539d.jpg%2F9VvyHEmzcGfM-duhwUoTS_cldzU7ZKMo9KHg6fSh4Ok%3Fv%3Dw1600r16_9&h=1ac07a09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有團體今午（13日）到尖沙咀地標「五枝旗桿」自行升旗，並用「殺他死」噴射印有曱甴圖案的紙張，抗議有人破壞國旗，並支持警察嚴正執法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3155224/org/84efa60c38dd4046fdfff68b38535927.jpg/l7r1S8Egxuu1-Vs7doV5p-srT626r7oKjgSRJo4EkSY?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3155224%2Forg%2F84efa60c38dd4046fdfff68b38535927.jpg%2Fl7r1S8Egxuu1-Vs7doV5p-srT626r7oKjgSRJo4EkSY%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=fd0c2e09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聲稱要發揚「愛國愛家」精神的團體「同心護港」今午（13日）到尖沙咀海港城地標「五枝旗桿」自行升旗，並在旗桿附近地上放置印有卡通曱甴圖案的紙張，然後用「殺他死」不斷噴射，抗議近日疑有反修例示威者破壞國旗，支持警察嚴正執法。<br />\n<br />\n活動約有四十人出席，在場所見，不少參與人士用普通話溝通，也有路過中國內地遊客即興參與，有<span style=\"color: red;\">人唱國歌、紅歌，亦有人不斷叫「中國共產黨萬歲」等口號。<br />\n</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3155218/org/feba27267f0a2b41e8195ed331dc2e67.jpg/S_Pj33kU7lu8pokcHm6OfNFLBmQUz9_F0pZgZNKWYGQ?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3155218%2Forg%2Ffeba27267f0a2b41e8195ed331dc2e67.jpg%2FS_Pj33kU7lu8pokcHm6OfNFLBmQUz9_F0pZgZNKWYGQ%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=b3b30bf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n受近日事件影響，「五枝旗桿」被圍欄封阻，並沒有旗幟。參加者爬上旗桿底放置自備的國旗，在活動完畢後卻重新把國旗除下拿走。<br />\n<br />\n團體召集人，報稱為的士司機的曹達明表示：「自政府「反修例」以來有很多黑衣暴徒破壞國旗，犯了香港國旗法，今日的目的是令破壞國旗的人知道這是國家的地方，不容他們搗亂。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3155214/org/002fee137b83f3223fe3f6f881153f15.jpg/Bq96rMyt6yf47mejVBoFNdSM6Nm6tFktKq6I2SquiNk?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3155214%2Forg%2F002fee137b83f3223fe3f6f881153f15.jpg%2FBq96rMyt6yf47mejVBoFNdSM6Nm6tFktKq6I2SquiNk%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=8c8404e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被問到有女示威者被射爆眼，他認為醫生未有公佈傷勢，所以有理由懷疑她是不敢講出被自己人打傷的真相，而東區醫院醫護人員抗議是因受到不實報導影響。他亦認為過期催淚彈沒有殺傷力，只是影響準繩度。曹亦向外國遊客叫囂「get out」，卻在訪問時表示支持旅遊業。<br />\n<br />\n參加者郭先生從朋友電話得知活動，專程來到表達訴求，「對曱甴要殺他死」，亦有中國內地遊客激動地表示：「看見國旗，聽見國歌就當然要留下來。」"},{"pid":"4cb6c2e2c38836896db228c103325ec6f9f3394a","tid":1463112,"uid":246118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:10:03.000Z","msg":"曹亦向外國遊客叫囂「get out」，卻在訪問時表示支持旅遊業。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19845f1a76c7f21c1d1cab53a1bb216a124595fb","tid":1463112,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:10:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">曹亦向外國遊客叫囂「get out」，卻在訪問時表示支持旅遊業</span></span>"},{"pid":"22d0e3d9679022f74af8ea6d135032f9a6464428","tid":1463112,"uid":235527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:10:43.000Z","msg":"咳突支那style"},{"pid":"0f53e5e577f6c3b40389ef6816c952463eec0a09","tid":1463112,"uid":305822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:14:17.000Z","msg":"點解冇人推816曬錢行動？！借位sor<br />\n816 經濟制裁 殺人政權(2) (附教學，後面精彩撚藍屍睇曬佢！）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1462757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1462757</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}